WEBVTT

00:01:32.820 --> 00:01:37.440
[Return of the Queen]

00:01:38.490 --> 00:01:40.350
[Episode 15]

00:02:07.380 --> 00:02:08.419
♪ Counting down ♪

00:02:08.750 --> 00:02:09.910
♪ How long has it been? ♪

00:02:10.280 --> 00:02:12.770
♪ I've wound myself up tight
just to see her ♪

00:02:13.100 --> 00:02:13.120
♪ What she loves ♪

00:02:13.120 --> 00:02:14.280
Ye Haimeng.

00:02:14.610 --> 00:02:15.000
♪ What she hates ♪

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:15.840
Haimeng!

00:02:15.870 --> 00:02:18.350
♪ Fill up the whole notebook
with her likes and dislikes ♪

00:02:18.630 --> 00:02:18.690
What's wrong?

00:02:18.690 --> 00:02:19.360
♪ Secretly ♪

00:02:19.360 --> 00:02:19.800
Find—

00:02:20.120 --> 00:02:21.240
♪ Write a song ♪

00:02:21.590 --> 00:02:22.410
♪ Sing it to her ♪

00:02:22.740 --> 00:02:23.960
♪ She can't help but giggle ♪

00:02:24.540 --> 00:02:25.690
♪ Every single day ♪

00:02:25.880 --> 00:02:27.120
♪ I wanna show her off
to the whole world ♪

00:02:27.120 --> 00:02:27.520
Ling Ke,

00:02:27.520 --> 00:02:28.000
don't go!

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:28.680
Ling Ke,

00:02:28.680 --> 00:02:29.140
let's go.

00:02:29.140 --> 00:02:29.910
♪ She's like ♪

00:02:30.470 --> 00:02:30.590
Let's go.

00:02:30.590 --> 00:02:33.840
♪ Honey kissed by the sun ♪

00:02:34.850 --> 00:02:35.790
♪ Tastes so sweet ♪

00:02:36.310 --> 00:02:39.820
♪ But never too much ♪

00:02:42.070 --> 00:02:44.040
♪ Secrets at the corner of her smile ♪

00:02:44.920 --> 00:02:47.950
♪ One little taste,
and I'm already hooked ♪

00:03:02.000 --> 00:03:03.560
You called Lu Siyu?

00:03:10.470 --> 00:03:11.000
You already knew

00:03:11.000 --> 00:03:12.530
about them being together?

00:03:12.590 --> 00:03:13.430
Just like you,

00:03:15.030 --> 00:03:16.160
I just saw it happen.

00:03:16.190 --> 00:03:17.400
It's no big deal

00:03:18.560 --> 00:03:19.750
that they're together.

00:03:19.750 --> 00:03:20.550
Not a big deal?

00:03:22.710 --> 00:03:24.120
Before Haimeng returned,

00:03:24.120 --> 00:03:25.280
she clearly told me

00:03:25.800 --> 00:03:26.590
the purpose of her return

00:03:26.590 --> 00:03:28.360
was to take back Mare Nubium

00:03:28.680 --> 00:03:30.079
and uncover the truth.

00:03:30.710 --> 00:03:32.000
But what is she doing now?

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:32.590
She and Lu Siyu—

00:03:32.590 --> 00:03:33.800
Haven't you already achieved

00:03:33.800 --> 00:03:35.030
what you planned?

00:03:35.030 --> 00:03:36.470
The truth you wanted

00:03:36.470 --> 00:03:38.030
has all come to light tonight.

00:03:38.030 --> 00:03:39.310
Come to light?

00:03:39.310 --> 00:03:40.190
Mare Nubium has already returned

00:03:40.190 --> 00:03:41.320
to Haimeng's hands.

00:03:41.750 --> 00:03:43.150
Tonight, you all saw

00:03:43.150 --> 00:03:45.240
that Lu Sinan had someone else he loved.

00:03:45.240 --> 00:03:46.280
That marriage

00:03:46.280 --> 00:03:46.960
was just a stepping stone

00:03:46.960 --> 00:03:48.820
to a scheme against the Ye family.

00:03:49.000 --> 00:03:49.750
Is that

00:03:50.590 --> 00:03:51.590
all there is to it?

00:03:51.590 --> 00:03:52.430
What else?

00:03:52.910 --> 00:03:53.910
Do you want Haimeng

00:03:53.910 --> 00:03:55.710
to be trapped in that marriage forever?

00:03:55.710 --> 00:03:56.400
Let alone that Sinan

00:03:56.400 --> 00:03:57.520
has been dead for four years,

00:03:57.520 --> 00:03:58.710
Haimeng was the victim

00:03:58.710 --> 00:04:00.150
in that marriage.

00:04:00.400 --> 00:04:01.150
Now that everything

00:04:01.150 --> 00:04:02.630
has come to light,

00:04:03.000 --> 00:04:04.560
as her cousin and friend,

00:04:05.240 --> 00:04:05.840
I hope she can

00:04:05.840 --> 00:04:07.240
let go of everything soon

00:04:07.520 --> 00:04:08.870
and return to her normal life.

00:04:08.870 --> 00:04:10.080
So your idea of letting her return
to a normal life

00:04:10.080 --> 00:04:10.910
is just watching her

00:04:10.910 --> 00:04:11.430
be with Lu Siyu?

00:04:11.430 --> 00:04:12.910
Isn't Siyu good enough?

00:04:18.240 --> 00:04:19.839
Between the two Lu brothers,

00:04:20.829 --> 00:04:22.920
I didn't have much contact with Sinan,

00:04:22.920 --> 00:04:24.380
but I know Siyu quite well.

00:04:25.000 --> 00:04:25.950
Although he is

00:04:25.950 --> 00:04:27.610
the youngest in the Lu family,

00:04:27.920 --> 00:04:29.430
he has always been pure.

00:04:29.430 --> 00:04:30.430
He's never been caught

00:04:30.430 --> 00:04:31.430
in the whirl of wealth,

00:04:31.430 --> 00:04:32.070
nor tainted

00:04:32.070 --> 00:04:33.600
by social games.

00:04:33.870 --> 00:04:34.720
Everything he has achieved—

00:04:34.720 --> 00:04:36.040
all his accomplishments and honors—

00:04:36.040 --> 00:04:37.390
is the result of his own effort.

00:04:37.390 --> 00:04:38.590
Isn't a Siyu like that

00:04:38.800 --> 00:04:40.200
truly worthy of Haimeng?

00:04:40.390 --> 00:04:41.360
Should we be discussing

00:04:41.360 --> 00:04:42.240
whether he is worthy

00:04:42.240 --> 00:04:42.870
or not worthy

00:04:42.870 --> 00:04:43.800
of Haimeng right now?

00:04:43.800 --> 00:04:45.000
Then what is the issue?

00:04:45.000 --> 00:04:46.040
Lu Sinan is a Lu,

00:04:46.040 --> 00:04:47.510
and so is Lu Siyu.

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:48.750
Someone from the Lu family

00:04:48.750 --> 00:04:50.409
has already crushed her once.

00:04:50.680 --> 00:04:51.680
Now that she has another shot,

00:04:51.680 --> 00:04:52.360
should she risk diving

00:04:52.360 --> 00:04:53.870
into the Lu family's fire again?

00:04:53.870 --> 00:04:55.600
Don't just look at
whether they're compatible or not

00:04:55.600 --> 00:04:56.870
on the surface.

00:04:57.159 --> 00:04:57.720
If you really are

00:04:57.720 --> 00:04:59.380
Haimeng's cousin and friend,

00:04:59.600 --> 00:05:01.000
you should persuade her

00:05:01.270 --> 00:05:03.630
to get out of the Lu family chaos
as soon as she can.

00:05:03.630 --> 00:05:04.830
Don't let her make

00:05:04.830 --> 00:05:06.510
the same mistake over and over again.

00:05:06.510 --> 00:05:07.070
But—

00:05:07.070 --> 00:05:07.800
Cut it out.

00:05:09.600 --> 00:05:11.460
I don't want to comment on Lu Siyu.

00:05:11.560 --> 00:05:13.000
And I don't want him to ever appear

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:14.400
in Haimeng's life again.

00:05:15.000 --> 00:05:15.680
That's it.

00:05:20.630 --> 00:05:21.390
Ling Ke.

00:05:22.040 --> 00:05:22.750
Ling Ke!

00:06:30.120 --> 00:06:30.870
Uncle Mo.

00:06:31.360 --> 00:06:32.490
Why have I never seen

00:06:32.680 --> 00:06:34.070
this painting before?

00:06:34.310 --> 00:06:36.159
Your brother commissioned it

00:06:36.600 --> 00:06:37.360
for Ms. Ye

00:06:37.360 --> 00:06:38.630
before their wedding.

00:06:39.190 --> 00:06:40.680
It was a token of love

00:06:40.680 --> 00:06:42.210
between Sinan and Haimeng?

00:06:42.600 --> 00:06:44.400
It's more than just a love token.

00:06:44.750 --> 00:06:45.720
It bound

00:06:45.720 --> 00:06:46.980
their fates together.

00:06:47.600 --> 00:06:48.560
[Fates.]

00:06:54.070 --> 00:06:54.950
[Sinan, look.]

00:06:54.950 --> 00:06:57.270
I won an excellence award
in this competition.

00:06:57.270 --> 00:06:59.430
[Just an excellence award isn't enough.]

00:06:59.430 --> 00:07:00.000
From now on, you

00:07:00.000 --> 00:07:02.060
must only bring back championships.

00:07:02.870 --> 00:07:04.390
[This little butterfly]

00:07:04.390 --> 00:07:05.720
[will serve as your motivation.]

00:07:05.720 --> 00:07:07.360
[When you win
all the league championships,]

00:07:07.360 --> 00:07:08.630
[only then can you take it off.]

00:07:08.630 --> 00:07:09.560
[One day, you'll be]

00:07:09.560 --> 00:07:10.600
[the most accomplished
among the Lu family.]

00:07:10.600 --> 00:07:11.950
[You'll bring home]

00:07:11.950 --> 00:07:13.240
[the most, the best,]

00:07:13.240 --> 00:07:14.430
[the most dazzling championships.]

00:07:14.430 --> 00:07:15.870
I believe you can do it,

00:07:16.480 --> 00:07:16.800
right?

00:07:16.800 --> 00:07:17.720
[He has never treated you]

00:07:17.720 --> 00:07:19.480
[as a real brother.]

00:07:19.800 --> 00:07:20.920
[Lu Sinan]

00:07:21.360 --> 00:07:22.070
[was never]

00:07:22.070 --> 00:07:24.400
[the perfect brother you thought he was.]

00:07:24.430 --> 00:07:25.830
[Nor was he the perfect husband]

00:07:25.830 --> 00:07:27.000
[others believed him to be.]

00:07:27.000 --> 00:07:29.510
[He's just like everyone else
in your Lu family.]

00:07:29.510 --> 00:07:32.000
[For the sake
of the Ye family's Mare Nubium,]

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:33.430
[he tried to kill me]

00:07:33.920 --> 00:07:36.560
[in the name of marriage.]

00:07:39.560 --> 00:07:40.430
[Why?]

00:07:41.159 --> 00:07:41.630
[Lu Sinan,]

00:07:41.630 --> 00:07:43.310
[why did you do that?]

00:07:44.190 --> 00:07:45.270
[Lu Sinan.]

00:07:46.070 --> 00:07:47.480
[Lu Sinan.]

00:07:49.159 --> 00:07:50.040
[Brother.]

00:08:27.270 --> 00:08:28.160
[Lu Siyu,]

00:08:28.510 --> 00:08:29.240
[come home.]

00:08:41.549 --> 00:08:42.360
Siyu,

00:08:42.909 --> 00:08:43.270
come.

00:08:43.870 --> 00:08:44.400
Sit down.

00:08:51.720 --> 00:08:52.390
Chen Mo.

00:08:58.200 --> 00:08:59.840
The chairman is already aware of

00:08:59.840 --> 00:09:01.030
the recent family incidents.

00:09:01.030 --> 00:09:02.320
This time, he returned from the sanatorium

00:09:02.320 --> 00:09:03.670
specifically to address family matters.

00:09:03.670 --> 00:09:04.630
Therefore,

00:09:04.630 --> 00:09:05.360
I will now announce

00:09:05.360 --> 00:09:07.150
the following decisions on his behalf:

00:09:07.150 --> 00:09:08.630
Starting tomorrow, Siyue and Jiang Lin

00:09:08.630 --> 00:09:09.720
will move out

00:09:09.720 --> 00:09:10.650
of the Lu Mansion

00:09:10.910 --> 00:09:12.200
and establish their own household.

00:09:12.200 --> 00:09:13.320
Jiang Lin can come with me

00:09:13.320 --> 00:09:14.080
to Changlu

00:09:14.320 --> 00:09:16.520
and become a member of Changlu Capital.

00:09:17.630 --> 00:09:18.360
Siyu,

00:09:18.910 --> 00:09:20.000
you are

00:09:20.000 --> 00:09:22.080
to liquidate all domestic investments
within this week.

00:09:22.080 --> 00:09:22.910
Next week, someone will escort you

00:09:22.910 --> 00:09:23.770
back overseas.

00:09:24.790 --> 00:09:25.840
As for Madam,

00:09:26.870 --> 00:09:28.030
lawyers will assist you

00:09:28.030 --> 00:09:30.290
in completing the divorce proceedings.

00:09:30.600 --> 00:09:32.130
Please leave the Lu family.

00:09:32.750 --> 00:09:34.150
You want to drive me away?

00:09:36.840 --> 00:09:38.720
As the Lu family's mistress,

00:09:39.670 --> 00:09:42.200
you have neither run
the household responsibly

00:09:42.200 --> 00:09:44.200
nor raised your children properly,

00:09:44.320 --> 00:09:45.870
and you even instigated Sinan

00:09:45.870 --> 00:09:47.600
to commit horrible deeds.

00:09:48.320 --> 00:09:49.910
How can the Lu family keep you?

00:09:49.910 --> 00:09:51.270
I instigated him?

00:09:52.030 --> 00:09:53.430
Do you have any evidence?

00:09:53.750 --> 00:09:54.600
Lu Sinan is your son

00:09:54.600 --> 00:09:55.750
with your ex-wife.

00:09:55.750 --> 00:09:56.360
All these years,

00:09:56.360 --> 00:09:57.790
he never treated me as his mother.

00:09:57.790 --> 00:09:59.600
He only held resentment toward me.

00:09:59.600 --> 00:10:01.200
He's the eldest son of the Lu family—

00:10:01.200 --> 00:10:02.670
why would I try to manipulate him?

00:10:02.670 --> 00:10:04.440
And why would he even listen to me?

00:10:04.440 --> 00:10:06.390
So now that Sinan is gone,

00:10:06.870 --> 00:10:08.470
you're pushing all the blame

00:10:08.550 --> 00:10:10.080
onto him?

00:10:10.080 --> 00:10:11.270
What blame am I pushing onto him?

00:10:11.270 --> 00:10:13.080
Did I force him
to fall in love with Ye Haimeng,

00:10:13.080 --> 00:10:13.960
or did I force him

00:10:13.960 --> 00:10:15.120
to marry her?

00:10:17.960 --> 00:10:20.080
It was your precious eldest son

00:10:20.360 --> 00:10:22.320
who plotted against
the Ye's only daughter,

00:10:22.320 --> 00:10:23.390
doing everything he could

00:10:23.390 --> 00:10:24.840
to trick her into marriage,

00:10:24.840 --> 00:10:26.720
and then using marital rights

00:10:26.720 --> 00:10:28.120
to seize her family's fortune.

00:10:28.120 --> 00:10:29.240
These were all

00:10:29.240 --> 00:10:30.240
Lu Sinan's own plans.

00:10:30.240 --> 00:10:31.480
What does it have to do with me?

00:10:31.480 --> 00:10:32.960
Nothing to do with you?

00:10:33.480 --> 00:10:34.940
That's easy for you to say.

00:10:35.150 --> 00:10:36.880
If you had nothing to do with it,

00:10:36.910 --> 00:10:37.600
then why did Ye Haimeng

00:10:37.600 --> 00:10:38.840
come looking for you?

00:10:39.120 --> 00:10:40.270
Why did Ye Haimeng present

00:10:40.270 --> 00:10:41.390
at Lu Sinan's funeral

00:10:41.390 --> 00:10:43.000
with so much evidence?

00:10:43.240 --> 00:10:44.790
And why was that evidence

00:10:44.790 --> 00:10:46.080
all over the news?

00:10:46.080 --> 00:10:47.510
Are you blind,

00:10:47.510 --> 00:10:48.750
or am I blind?

00:10:48.750 --> 00:10:50.210
Or is everyone else blind?

00:10:50.360 --> 00:10:51.960
The reporters made it all up.

00:10:51.960 --> 00:10:53.550
Siyue and I didn't do anything.

00:10:53.550 --> 00:10:54.600
We were just following

00:10:54.600 --> 00:10:55.510
Sinan's will

00:10:55.510 --> 00:10:57.200
and handling his funeral arrangements.

00:10:57.200 --> 00:10:58.670
Yet you, his own father,

00:10:58.670 --> 00:11:00.000
show no gratitude

00:11:00.000 --> 00:11:01.150
and pin all the blame

00:11:01.150 --> 00:11:02.510
on me.

00:11:02.510 --> 00:11:03.550
It's no surprise Sinan could do

00:11:03.550 --> 00:11:04.550
something like that,

00:11:04.550 --> 00:11:06.200
given a father like you.

00:11:06.200 --> 00:11:06.910
What did you say?

00:11:06.910 --> 00:11:07.670
I said,

00:11:07.910 --> 00:11:08.960
all these years

00:11:08.960 --> 00:11:10.960
you've neglected to discipline Lu Sinan.

00:11:10.960 --> 00:11:12.080
You didn't even know

00:11:12.080 --> 00:11:13.030
he got married

00:11:13.030 --> 00:11:13.840
or had children,

00:11:13.840 --> 00:11:14.960
matters of such importance.

00:11:14.960 --> 00:11:16.600
That's why he dared to murder

00:11:16.600 --> 00:11:17.910
someone else's daughter.

00:11:17.910 --> 00:11:19.150
What nonsense are you talking about?

00:11:19.150 --> 00:11:20.600
I'm not talking nonsense.

00:11:20.600 --> 00:11:22.870
A father who fails to guide his son
is to blame.

00:11:22.870 --> 00:11:24.910
Every single one of Lu Sinan's schemes
to murder his wife

00:11:24.910 --> 00:11:26.320
came from you!

00:11:26.630 --> 00:11:27.240
You...

00:11:27.550 --> 00:11:28.630
Don't hit my mom!

00:11:54.240 --> 00:11:54.840
Dad.

00:11:55.910 --> 00:11:56.870
All these years,

00:11:57.600 --> 00:11:59.320
you've been completely focused on
Changlu Group,

00:11:59.320 --> 00:12:00.480
while all the household matters

00:12:00.480 --> 00:12:02.210
have been handled by Mom alone.

00:12:02.960 --> 00:12:04.910
The Lu family has survived until now

00:12:04.910 --> 00:12:06.670
thanks entirely to Mom.

00:12:08.670 --> 00:12:10.120
How could you say

00:12:10.750 --> 00:12:12.720
that Sinan was instigated by Mom?

00:12:15.200 --> 00:12:16.000
Yes,

00:12:16.790 --> 00:12:18.480
Mom is your second wife.

00:12:18.480 --> 00:12:20.030
So since she first arrived,

00:12:20.720 --> 00:12:22.030
Sinan never once

00:12:22.030 --> 00:12:22.890
called her Mom.

00:12:23.120 --> 00:12:23.840
How could he possibly

00:12:23.840 --> 00:12:25.360
have listened to her?

00:12:27.320 --> 00:12:28.840
On the contrary, Lu Sinan

00:12:29.790 --> 00:12:31.360
never considered us

00:12:31.360 --> 00:12:33.030
his family.

00:12:34.910 --> 00:12:36.360
I still remember

00:12:37.510 --> 00:12:39.170
how much he hated me as a child.

00:12:39.600 --> 00:12:40.840
He even said

00:12:41.600 --> 00:12:42.800
that in the next life,

00:12:43.080 --> 00:12:43.790
he still wouldn't recognize us

00:12:43.790 --> 00:12:45.150
as siblings.

00:12:46.480 --> 00:12:47.910
And when it comes to Siyu,

00:12:49.030 --> 00:12:50.230
he went even further.

00:12:51.790 --> 00:12:54.440
Sinan always hated Siyu the most.

00:12:54.790 --> 00:12:56.630
Don't you all know that?

00:13:02.600 --> 00:13:04.330
Siyu was just a little kid then.

00:13:04.630 --> 00:13:06.320
He didn't understand anything.

00:13:06.320 --> 00:13:07.480
But I did.

00:13:07.790 --> 00:13:09.270
Since Siyu was seven,

00:13:10.080 --> 00:13:11.630
he kept telling Uncle Mo

00:13:12.360 --> 00:13:14.160
to kick Siyu out of the Lu family.

00:13:14.360 --> 00:13:16.240
He never wanted Siyu
to have the Lu surname,

00:13:16.240 --> 00:13:17.360
or to get his hands on

00:13:17.360 --> 00:13:18.690
the Lu family business.

00:13:19.790 --> 00:13:21.750
All that talk about archery championships

00:13:21.750 --> 00:13:23.510
and bringing honor to the family—

00:13:23.510 --> 00:13:24.910
those were just excuses.

00:13:25.360 --> 00:13:26.200
He didn't want

00:13:26.200 --> 00:13:27.630
Siyu to stay in China.

00:13:27.630 --> 00:13:29.910
He hated his half-brother,
the son of his stepmother.

00:13:29.910 --> 00:13:31.480
He hated Siyu!

00:13:34.270 --> 00:13:35.120
Chen Mo,

00:13:36.510 --> 00:13:37.750
what Siyue said

00:13:38.670 --> 00:13:39.600
is all true?

00:13:40.030 --> 00:13:41.630
Sinan

00:13:41.630 --> 00:13:43.560
indeed didn't like Siyu very much.

00:13:43.790 --> 00:13:44.790
Probably because

00:13:45.630 --> 00:13:47.290
they have different mothers.

00:13:53.720 --> 00:13:55.670
There's no need to act this way.

00:13:56.120 --> 00:13:58.180
Of the three children in this family,

00:13:58.200 --> 00:14:00.080
which one have you ever truly cared for?

00:14:00.080 --> 00:14:01.000
The Lu family

00:14:01.000 --> 00:14:02.720
has come to this today

00:14:04.360 --> 00:14:05.840
all because of you.

