00:21:02.350 --> 00:21:03.550
you were following me

00:21:04.310 --> 00:21:05.310
for a long time.

00:21:08.070 --> 00:21:08.640
Haimeng,

00:21:09.070 --> 00:21:09.400
I...

00:21:09.400 --> 00:21:10.270
Relax.

00:21:11.240 --> 00:21:12.160
Today,

00:21:12.160 --> 00:21:12.750
I won't

00:21:12.750 --> 00:21:14.350
pursue this matter with you.

00:21:14.720 --> 00:21:16.200
Go ahead with your plans.

00:21:16.590 --> 00:21:17.680
When I need to,

00:21:18.200 --> 00:21:18.930
I'll ask you.

00:21:25.920 --> 00:21:27.050
In the past few days,

00:21:27.270 --> 00:21:29.680
the Lu family has gone through
major changes.

00:21:29.680 --> 00:21:30.940
Do you know about them?

