Du Meiyun was ordered by Lu Changdong

00:21:33.720 --> 00:21:35.350
to divorce and leave the family.

00:21:35.350 --> 00:21:36.270
Lu Siyue and Jiang Lin

00:21:36.270 --> 00:21:38.330
have also moved out of the Lu Mansion.

00:21:38.750 --> 00:21:39.720
Tonight,

00:21:40.440 --> 00:21:42.000
the youngest son of the Lu family,

00:21:42.000 --> 00:21:42.750
Lu Siyu,

00:21:43.110 --> 00:21:44.030
will be sent abroad

00:21:44.030 --> 00:21:45.490
by Lu Changdong's people.

00:21:48.480 --> 00:21:49.640
What a mess.

