There's still Chen Mo.

00:21:59.680 --> 00:22:00.940
Chen Mo is still there.

00:22:04.000 --> 00:22:05.260
Aren't you surprised?

00:22:06.830 --> 00:22:08.090
Surprised about what?

00:22:09.680 --> 00:22:11.480
The youngest son of the Lu family

00:22:11.590 --> 00:22:12.310
is leaving.

00:22:16.790 --> 00:22:18.350
No need to beat around the bush.

00:22:18.350 --> 00:22:19.680
