00:22:28.750 --> 00:22:29.920
That night,

00:22:29.920 --> 00:22:31.240
in that moment,

00:22:31.240 --> 00:22:32.270
I wanted to kiss him,

00:22:32.270 --> 00:22:33.030
so I did.

00:22:34.030 --> 00:22:35.360
I didn't care who he was,

00:22:35.720 --> 00:22:36.550
or whether

00:22:36.830 --> 00:22:38.440
he was Lu Sinan's brother.

00:22:38.720 --> 00:22:39.550
Haimeng,

00:22:39.550 --> 00:22:40.750
I know you don't care,

00:22:41.200 --> 00:22:42.790
but others definitely will.

00:22:42.790 --> 00:22:43.720
The Lu family

00:22:43.720 --> 00:22:44.960
will certainly care.

00:22:45.640 --> 00:22:46.640
My business

00:22:46.920 --> 00:22:48.580
has nothing to do with others.

00:22:48.640 --> 00:22:50.700
I've already reclaimed Mare Nubium,

00:22:50.880 --> 00:22:51.640
and I have no ties

00:22:51.640 --> 00:22:52.790
to Lu Sinan anymore.

00:22:53.440 --> 00:22:54.590
What I need to do now

00:22:55.110 --> 00:22:56.830
is to live my own life well.

00:22:56.830 --> 00:22:58.560
I don't care what others think.

00:22:58.960 --> 00:23:00.680
I only follow my heart.

00:23:01.270 --> 00:23:02.590
If I'm good to someone,

00:23:03.400 --> 00:23:05.110
it's only because I want to be.

00:23:05.680 --> 00:23:07.160
If I like someone,

00:23:08.000 --> 00:23:09.200
it's simply

00:23:10.200 --> 00:23:11.330
because I like them.

00:23:12.200 --> 00:23:13.160
Haimeng,

00:23:13.510 --> 00:23:13.880
I...

00:23:13.880 --> 00:23:14.790
Don't worry.

