00:26:03.920 --> 00:26:04.830
But

00:26:06.000 --> 00:26:07.550
aside from resenting him,

00:26:08.880 --> 00:26:09.790
I don't understand either

00:26:09.790 --> 00:26:11.000
what Sinan's deeper motive was

00:26:11.000 --> 00:26:11.720
for doing this

00:26:11.720 --> 00:26:13.350
in the first place.

